        'EDGE CASES: $5 minimum bet with odd $2.50 BJ payout — casino provides $0.50 or $1 chips. Multi-hand splits: each split hand has independent payout. If the dealer mis-pays and the error is caught before the next hand, the excess is recovered. If caught after the next hand begins, the error usually stands. Tournament payouts may use different ratios (1:1 on BJ is common in tournaments).'
